IT’S BETTER TO HAVE A PARTNER THAN GO ALONE 👭 today I was invited to talk about community at the @nubyenbeauty birthday celebration + it was an HONOUR❗️ THIS STUFF DOESN’T HAPPEN OVERNIGHT. ⛽️ so thankful to all of you for showing up, for engaging, for listening! So good to meet so many lovely women. Thank you LOLA. what a wonderful human you are. + to my homegirl @adnanamakeup for supporting me like always. 🦋 #modelme #nubyenbeauty ps. Does anyone remember bebo.com? 🤣🤣🤣
